{"tid":1673614,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［文學突發］胡蘭成都支持攬炒，同核彈都唔割！！！","createTime":"2019-10-24T17:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T07:09:27.000Z","uid":167634,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4a3eb5973286320c5f6ae032b18218a983a067b0","tid":1673614,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T17:48:05.000Z","msg":"《今生今世》<br />\n原序：<br />\n<br />\n       新近我濃愁如酒，不知要怎樣纔好，就索性不負責任，長日只去街上遊蕩，如為中學生時。隨後忽然又彷彿想明白了，且連這一晌的自暴自棄亦覺得是好的。<br />\n<br />\n       <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">縱使不能這樣快就打倒中共</span></span></strong>，我亦不焦急了。我而且賞識他的好處，如賞識秦始皇的造萬里長城，與其新法，棄灰者有刑。他將來被打倒，亦只是四時之序，功成者去。<br />\n<br />\n       《今生今世》是愛玲取的書名，我來日本後所寫。寫的是中國民間，江山有思。<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對共產黨，是將來勝負之機，決於一髮。且尚須度得過核兵器的世界戰爭的劫數。然中國即使劫後只剩了十萬人，亦文明依然可以再建的。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n       此書承水野勝太郎先生千金然諾，始得出版，使我感激，而亦感慨。這裏我還謝謝服部轍君於排印時為我校對。<br />\n<br />\n       水野先生所做的亦不容易，他說是三分人事七分天，而因尚有著七分天意，所以人事倒也急切不得窮絕。我此書便亦如曹孟德的詩的終篇、「幸甚至哉，歌以言志。」<br />\n<br />\n今生今世！<br />\n仲唔係靠我地？<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span></strong><br />\nP.S 胡蘭成亦有著作《革命要詩與學問》<br />\n文學家們，學者們<br />\n你地幾時先會好似五四運動咁行出黎，魯迅、周作人、蔡元培佢地企出黎呀！係你地教曉我地認識佢地架！"},{"pid":"25e3021128433c0b9b20344a376ccf915cb1c8a3","tid":1673614,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T17:48:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b3a2e10744883c789e7df80c2c51d464b9c2bb98","tid":1673614,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T17:48:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f05ae69ccbe4c82604fba35332b1ad09db5a471","tid":1673614,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T17:48:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/itbR4in.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FitbR4in.jpg&h=bd7ae3e5&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"91bd745131844e56c766218114532b29d1791625","tid":1673614,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T17:48:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea17392cb4f97f1f4482d0e37ddbe2c6d8bc757e","tid":1673614,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T17:48:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e27995c39fba795d8bd6d7b4de6370fe7b7b60d9","tid":1673614,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T17:49:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">11月2維園見！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"0bbe39fbadad5b330a0e214d214f47036eeeaedd","tid":1673614,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T17:49:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"90926db1ea740038becb3338c6279990fdb4de51","tid":1673614,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T17:49:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79207630c95a0635d7b75940827060cf80b102c3","tid":1673614,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T17:50:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a75f6f9670230e89cb9b03b0667a4fa8f1e54e1","tid":1673614,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T17:50:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e61d91ea9eb85db6253440a36a705b0057053a67","tid":1673614,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T17:50:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d8cd46bd318eda9b648b8a65f21f102cb6e1e149","tid":1673614,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T17:50:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5205799d20055dba4226ac8870e7e7b75d06c554","tid":1673614,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T17:50:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"82a892884dec7fc63c9aae6457c1de52c73fef1b","tid":1673614,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T17:54:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f7d26f69bc855d142593038